short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A chrome extension to enhance the React.dev with advanced topics

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: react.dev is the source of truth when learning React, but it only contains the basics. This extension adds links of advanced topics into react.dev so we can Dive Deeper into how React works.
